{"tid":225786,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【預告片】有冇巴絲想睇 新恐怖片「逃出絕命鎮」?","createTime":"2017-05-02T04:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T00:41:34.000Z","uid":41953,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"12cfaa6b2d1777aad4af8ac6530cf4686c519077","tid":225786,"uid":41953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T04:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/65226/590179c3eb150.gif?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F65226%2F590179c3eb150.gif%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=0e2006a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個故事講個黑人男主<br />\n比個白人壞女朋友引左返美國鄉下屋企見家長<br />\n<br />\n原來班人捉黑鬼去大腦改造<br />\n等啲想做黑鬼既老白鬼 或者身體有事眼盲既<br />\n可以換一個身體永續生命<br />\n白鬼屋企果兩個一男一女黑鬼<br />\n其實係佢地爺爺同麻麻<br />\n已經做左手術額頭有疤<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">但因為手術限制 原本黑鬼既意識仲會殘留係佢身體入面<br />\n只要一有閃光燈就會短暫拎返身體控制權</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n白鬼老婆係催眠大師 可以催眠黑鬼令佢地控制唔到自己身體<br />\n<br />\n最後白鬼一家陷家剷比黑鬼一條友殺哂<br />\n黑鬼個朋友開警車接佢走<br />\n<br />\n片頭果個黑鬼係其中一個比條白鬼婆引去改造大腦既人<br />\n想走但無車匙搵唔到<br />\n最後比人捉返返去<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4-S9Vo9UF94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4-S9Vo9UF94&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PZnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=7a6fc279\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4-S9Vo9UF94</a>"},{"pid":"495d307dc19ad39ec0128b9abc4375f32901bcc7","tid":225786,"uid":41953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T04:56:55.000Z","msg":"好睇"},{"pid":"6c4690426c7eb189511354e00cf9e2c21abbcd3c","tid":225786,"uid":41953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T04:59:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5752e8facc1ecb9bdd5848550bb4d5fe9b6fdcb","tid":225786,"uid":41953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-